title: Listen children, you do not deserve your damn S rank
body:
https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=0jgrCKhxE1s

You must take what you do not deserve from the grips of utter impossibility.
You must kill the unkillable and stop the unstoppable
You must farm minions like no other
You must destroy towers in your wake
The heavens must part in fear of your warpath

If you have time to question why you didn't get an S that means you aren't busy fapping to the amazing game you just played. Fuck you, you deserve nothing and hopefully got nothing if this is the case! That you got an S should be surprising because you are so damn high on how hard you were winning. There should be tigerblood pumping through your viens our out of your worn fingers. Everyone on your team should be worshipping you as a hero or demon. 

If all you can even do to complain about it is to post a damn picture of your kda then why would anyone write a book about your glorious conquest? That's pathetic. 

You didn't get an S because you don't deserve an S. Go practice or throw your face at more games until you stop being weak!
